quotes.quote: We as a group... I think this was the last time...
Remember the trip... we cycled something on top of a single rail...
We were pretty technical also.... for our age...
My goto pic for wishing you a birthday...
Rose day... it was not though...
Cheers to a younger you... we could have met early, then fun would have started early...
Imagine me editing this pic and placing someones hand holding your head...
I deserve a pic like this...
That class was too bright for images....
Look woh's clicking... Looking good all three of you..
We look decent enough, for a bunch of hooligans.... :D
Paddle to kiya nahi ek baar bhi, bas baith ke ghum liya....
That Dog was very fond of you...which is a good thing!!!

Thanks for everything, to the girls team of batch 2018. We couldn't have done it without you being there for us... 
Special thanks to you for leading that team...
